<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Haggard" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Haggard,</orth> a wild, untrained hawk: <bibl n="shak. ado 3.1.36" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 1, 36</bibl>. Shr. IV, <bibl n="shak. ado 1.196.36" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 196</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 4.2.39" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 39</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.1.71" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 1, 71</bibl>. Adjectively: <cit><quote>if I do prove her h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.260" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 3, 260</bibl></cit> (wild, untractable, unprincipled).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>